---
---

<section id="achievements">
    <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-number">03</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">Achievements Unlocked</h2>
        <div class="section-line"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="achievements-grid">
        <article class="achievement">
            <div class="achievement-icon gold">&#9733;</div>
            <div>
                <div class="achievement-title">App Store Spotlight</div>
                <div class="achievement-desc">Contributed to multiple apps featured in Apple&rsquo;s App Store editorial picks, including Warby Parker and Paperless Post.</div>
                <div class="achievement-year">Warby Parker &middot; Paperless Post</div>
            </div>
        </article>

        <article class="achievement">
            <div class="achievement-icon red">&#127942;</div>
            <div>
                <div class="achievement-title">BAFTA Award</div>
                <div class="achievement-desc">SongPop won the BAFTA for Social/Online Game. Music trivia played by millions worldwide.</div>
                <div class="achievement-year">FreshPlanet &mdash; 2013</div>
            </div>
        </article>

        <article class="achievement">
            <div class="achievement-icon teal">&#128293;</div>
            <div>
                <div class="achievement-title">Game Jam Streak</div>
                <div class="achievement-desc">Unbroken Global Game Jam streak since 2019, plus additional jams. New game every year, 48 hours, small teams.</div>
                <div class="achievement-year">2019 &mdash; Present</div>
            </div>
        </article>

        <article class="achievement">
            <div class="achievement-icon blue">&#128640;</div>
            <div>
                <div class="achievement-title">Zero to App Store</div>
                <div class="achievement-desc">Sole iOS engineer at Adapter. Built and shipped an AI assistant app from zero to App Store in under a year.</div>
                <div class="achievement-year">Adapter &mdash; 2025</div>
            </div>
        </article>

        <article class="achievement">
            <div class="achievement-icon gold">&#127979;</div>
            <div>
                <div class="achievement-title">Carnegie Mellon ETC</div>
                <div class="achievement-desc">Master&rsquo;s in Entertainment Technology. Games, technology, and storytelling.</div>
                <div class="achievement-year">Pittsburgh &rarr; NYC</div>
            </div>
        </article>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .achievements-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(320px, 1fr));
        gap: 1rem;
    }

    .achievement {
        display: flex;
        align-items: flex-start;
        gap: 1rem;
        padding: 1.25rem;
        background: var(--bg-card);
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 8px;
        transition: all 0.2s;
    }

    .achievement:hover {
        border-color: var(--border-hover);
        transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    .achievement-icon {
        width: 40px;
        height: 40px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .achievement-icon.gold {
        background: var(--accent-gold-glow);
    }

    .achievement-icon.teal {
        background: var(--accent-glow);
    }

    .achievement-icon.red {
        background: var(--accent-warm-glow);
    }

    .achievement-icon.blue {
        background: var(--accent-blue-glow);
    }

    .achievement-title {
        font-family: var(--display);
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-bottom: 0.2rem;
    }

    .achievement-desc {
        font-size: 0.78rem;
        color: var(--text-dim);
        line-height: 1.4;
    }

    .achievement-year {
        font-family: var(--mono);
        font-size: 0.6rem;
        color: var(--text-dim);
        margin-top: 0.4rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .achievements-grid {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        }
    }
</style>